ath !important;" xmlns="">\(y&lt;0\) </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000003903e159-085c-47a7-8737-71d07e2ad668 {margin-bottom: 0;line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;}span.pt-0000013903e159-085c-47a7-8737-71d07e2ad668 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000001dff9558-2998-40ed-a80a-2853b01ba28a" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(∴\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000011dff9558-2998-40ed-a80a-2853b01ba28a">  1g I 3q PZzf&#169;vM wg‡j †&#255;&#206;dj </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(=\frac{1}{2}\times 12π=6π\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000011dff9558-2998-40ed-a80a-2853b01ba28a"> eM&#169;GKK |</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000001dff9558-2998-40ed-a80a-2853b01ba28a {margin-bottom: 0;line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;}span.pt-0000011dff9558-2998-40ed-a80a-2853b01ba28a {font-family: SutonnyMJ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p></span>
