                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-00000073c5eb63-ad16-4eb8-9af6-25fa6c8e7488" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\({x}^{2}+{y}^{2}+2\times \frac{1}{6}x+2\times \frac{1}{6}y=0\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000173c5eb63-ad16-4eb8-9af6-25fa6c8e7488"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000073c5eb63-ad16-4eb8-9af6-25fa6c8e7488 {margin-bottom: 0;line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;}span.pt-00000173c5eb63-ad16-4eb8-9af6-25fa6c8e7488 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000005659d7fe-9260-43a2-84cd-e0bbfccef12b" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(∴\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000015659d7fe-9260-43a2-84cd-e0bbfccef12b"> †K›`&#170; </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(≡(-g,-f)≡\left(-\frac{1}{6},-\frac{1}{6}\right)\) </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000005659d7fe-9260-43a2-84cd-e0bbfccef12b {margin-bottom: 0;line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;}span.pt-0000015659d7fe-9260-43a2-84cd-e0bbfccef12b {font-family: SutonnyMJ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p></span>
